00:17:38.641 --> 00:17:39.433 align:middle line:90%
everything?

00:17:39.433 --> 00:17:40.309 align:middle line:84%
>>BEGICH: Or you
get to the point

00:17:40.309 --> 00:17:42.520 align:middle line:84%
where you go, well, those
aren't good memories.

00:17:42.520 --> 00:17:44.313 align:middle line:84%
Those aren't the
politically correct things

00:17:44.313 --> 00:17:45.773 align:middle line:84%
we want you to be
thinking about.

00:17:45.773 --> 00:17:46.899 align:middle line:90%
>> NOORY: Let's erase them.

00:17:46.899 --> 00:17:47.066 align:middle line:90%
>>BEGICH: Yeah.

00:17:47.066 --> 00:17:50.027 align:middle line:84%
When do we get to that point in
our society and in our culture?

00:17:50.027 --> 00:17:52.071 align:middle line:90%
And are we headed that way?

00:17:52.071 --> 00:17:55.950 align:middle line:84%
Are people more willing to give
up their personal sovereignty

00:17:55.950 --> 00:17:59.078 align:middle line:84%
in exchange for some
collective good?

00:17:59.078 --> 00:18:01.455 align:middle line:84%
This is where I think
where some of the anger,

00:18:01.455 --> 00:18:04.333 align:middle line:84%
too, comes in terms of how
our population looks at it.

00:18:04.333 --> 00:18:06.043 align:middle line:90%
Because we feel so manipulated.

00:18:06.043 --> 00:18:07.003 align:middle line:84%
I mean, you feel
manipulated every time

00:18:07.003 --> 00:18:08.504 align:middle line:90%
you turn on the television set.

00:18:08.504 --> 00:18:10.965 align:middle line:84%
Why is the media in
such bad rapport?

00:18:10.965 --> 00:18:13.801 align:middle line:84%
Because people don't
trust it anymore.

00:18:13.801 --> 00:18:14.969 align:middle line:90%
And there's a variety.

00:18:14.969 --> 00:18:16.679 align:middle line:84%
You can get any
information you want now.

00:18:16.679 --> 00:18:18.806 align:middle line:84%
You can go to the internet,
find anything you want.

00:18:18.806 --> 00:18:20.224 align:middle line:84%
You got the
worldwide mind, which

00:18:20.224 --> 00:18:21.934 align:middle line:90%
is really the next evolution.

00:18:21.934 --> 00:18:23.644 align:middle line:84%
Because if you read
the literature-- even

00:18:23.644 --> 00:18:25.563 align:middle line:90%
PBS is talking about this.

00:18:25.563 --> 00:18:27.523 align:middle line:84%
They have a special they
ran a number of years

00:18:27.523 --> 00:18:29.817 align:middle line:84%
ago called "The Worldwide
Mind," where they believe

00:18:29.817 --> 00:18:31.235 align:middle line:84%
the next evolution
of the internet

00:18:31.235 --> 00:18:32.695 align:middle line:84%
is where our minds
are all connected.

00:18:32.695 --> 00:18:34.030 align:middle line:90%
>> NOORY: They're all connected.

00:18:34.030 --> 00:18:34.822 align:middle line:90%
That's dangerous.

00:18:34.822 --> 00:18:37.283 align:middle line:84%
>>BEGICH: That's dangerous--
if it's done artificially,

00:18:37.283 --> 00:18:37.700 align:middle line:90%
because--

00:18:37.700 --> 00:18:39.660 align:middle line:84%
>> NOORY: Because what
if you sent a virus out?

00:18:39.660 --> 00:18:40.995 align:middle line:90%
>>BEGICH: Yeah, exactly right.

00:18:40.995 --> 00:18:43.331 align:middle line:84%
And what is that in
the 21st century?

00:18:43.331 --> 00:18:45.041 align:middle line:90%
And here's the thing.

00:18:45.041 --> 00:18:48.044 align:middle line:84%
We try to duplicate what
nature already does.

00:18:48.044 --> 00:18:49.462 align:middle line:90%
We already do this.

00:18:49.462 --> 00:18:51.505 align:middle line:84%
Most of our communication
functions that way,

00:18:51.505 --> 00:18:53.090 align:middle line:90%
although we don't perceive it.

00:18:53.090 --> 00:18:56.010 align:middle line:84%
The next evolution, the next
revolution in human thinking,

00:18:56.010 --> 00:18:58.888 align:middle line:84%
will be our own
evolution as we begin--

00:18:58.888 --> 00:19:00.765 align:middle line:84%
I mean, what's the
defense mechanism

00:19:00.765 --> 00:19:02.933 align:middle line:90%
about a rogue government?

00:19:02.933 --> 00:19:06.771 align:middle line:84%
Ultimately it's to
have transparency.

00:19:06.771 --> 00:19:08.397 align:middle line:84%
Some of the people
that I've met with,

00:19:08.397 --> 00:19:10.775 align:middle line:84%
one of the best biophysicists--
couple of best biophysicists

00:19:10.775 --> 00:19:12.276 align:middle line:84%
in the world say
this is where we're

00:19:12.276 --> 00:19:14.362 align:middle line:84%
headed, that there's
going to come a time,

00:19:14.362 --> 00:19:17.615 align:middle line:84%
maybe in our lifetimes, where
we see the next evolution begin

00:19:17.615 --> 00:19:21.118 align:middle line:84%
to manifest, which is
we all start to manifest

00:19:21.118 --> 00:19:22.995 align:middle line:90%
these unique capabilities.

00:19:22.995 --> 00:19:27.500 align:middle line:84%
>> NOORY: Well, MK-Ultra was set
up right to begin the process

00:19:27.500 --> 00:19:31.921 align:middle line:84%
of learning how to
control the human mind.

