a signal that would create

00:21:28.829 --> 00:21:32.041 align:middle line:84%
a general sense of dis-ease, of
anxiety across the population.

00:21:32.041 --> 00:21:33.292 align:middle line:90%
>> NOORY: Or well-being.

00:21:33.292 --> 00:21:34.418 align:middle line:90%
>>BEGICH: Or well-being.

00:21:34.418 --> 00:21:37.713 align:middle line:84%
And in this, then, you could,
say, take the 6 o'clock

00:21:37.713 --> 00:21:41.050 align:middle line:84%
