00:21:58.108 --> 00:22:00.819 align:middle line:84%
And this is why these
guys in that clip said,

00:22:00.819 --> 00:22:02.112 align:middle line:90%
oh, this is fun.

00:22:02.112 --> 00:22:02.905 align:middle line:90%
These are--

00:22:02.905 --> 00:22:03.989 align:middle line:90%
>> NOORY: Fun, fun, fun.

00:22:03.989 --> 00:22:05.157 align:middle line:90%
>>BEGICH: Fun, fun, fun.

00:22:05.157 --> 00:22:06.992 align:middle line:90%
What the heck?

00:22:06.992 --> 00:22:09.578 align:middle line:84%
And when you look at where these
guys came from, a lot of them

00:22:09.578 --> 00:22:11.997 align:middle line:84%
did-- several of this projects
were run through, of course,

00:22:11.997 --> 00:22:13.207 align:middle line:90%
Central Intelligence Agency.

00:22:13.207 --> 00:22:15.501 align:middle line:84%
But a lot of the experts they
got through organizations

00:22:15.501 --> 00:22:17.586 align:middle line:84%
like Mankind Research,
which was sort

00:22:17.586 --> 00:22:20.381 align:middle line:84%
of a front organization for a
bunch of maverick scientists

00:22:20.381 --> 00:22:23.467 align:middle line:84%
that didn't fit very well in
academia that the CIA funded

00:22:23.467 --> 00:22:27.721 align:middle line:84%
to do a bunch of pretty
odd, odd experiments.

00:22:27.721 --> 00:22:30.474 align:middle line:84%
In fact, one of the
guys that was involved,

00:22:30.474 --> 00:22:33.852 align:middle line:84%
and that was his Northwest
field director for those guys,

00:22:33.852 --> 00:22:34.645 align:middle line:90%
I got to know.

00:22:34.645 --> 00:22:38.732 align:middle line:84%
And he was heavily involved
in the occult in the '60s, was

00:22:38.732 --> 00:22:42.236 align:middle line:84%
deeply involved, but he's also
a very bright guy, a genius.

00:22:42.236 --> 00:22:43.737 align:middle line:90%
And so they brought him in.

00:22:43.737 --> 00:22:48.951 align:middle line:84%
And this guy developed protocols
for enhancing ESP potentials,

00:22:48.951 --> 00:22:51.912 align:middle line:84%
being able to be more right
on your guessing or improving

00:22:51.912 --> 00:22:53.038 align:middle line:90%
intuition.

