That all became part of the
Navy SEALs program of training

00:22:56.959 --> 00:22:59.211 align:middle line:84%
to get that kind of into
intuitive-- do you turn left?

00:22:59.211 --> 00:23:00.588 align:middle line:90%
Do you turn right?

00:23:00.588 --> 00:23:03.257 align:middle line:84%
These are things that innately
we all have-- we've all

00:23:03.257 --> 00:23:04.341 align:middle line:90%
experienced in our lives.

00:23:04.341 --> 00:23:05.551 align:middle line:90%
>> NOORY: It's in our system.

00:23:05.551 --> 00:23:07.011 align:middle line:84%
>>BEGICH: Yeah, we've
experienced these things

00:23:07.011 --> 00:23:09.680 align:middle line:84%
where we've had that leap, where
you knew what the other guy was

00:23:09.680 --> 00:23:12.850 align:middle line:84%
thinking, and it wasn't just
a coincidence, or where you've

00:23:12.850 --> 00:23:14.727 align:middle line:90%
had these unusual experiences.

00:23:14.727 --> 00:23:15.644 align:middle line:90%
And I've had my own.

00:23:15.644 --> 00:23:16.937 align:middle line:90%
>> NOORY: More than hunches.

00:23:16.937 --> 00:23:17.730 align:middle line:90%
>>BEGICH: Yeah.

00:23:17.730 --> 00:23:20.816 align:middle line:84%
And I've had some that
were so profound that they

00:23:20.816 --> 00:23:24.695 align:middle line:84%
defy any other explanation
but to say that information,

00:23:24.695 --> 00:23:25.738 align:middle line:90%
that transfer is real.

00:23:25.738 --> 00:23:28.866 align:middle line:84%
Now, a good friend of mine, a
physicist Elizabeth Rauscher,

00:23:28.866 --> 00:23:30.784 align:middle line:84%
her and her late husband
Bill Bise actually

00:23:30.784 --> 00:23:33.454 align:middle line:84%
developed an
apparatus to transfer

00:23:33.454 --> 00:23:35.164 align:middle line:84%
thought from one
person to another.

00:23:35.164 --> 00:23:35.956 align:middle line:90%
>> NOORY: Can it be done?

00:23:35.956 --> 00:23:36.999 align:middle line:90%
>>BEGICH: It can be done.

00:23:36.999 --> 00:23:39.627 align:middle line:84%
And I have her
unpublished paper on this.

00:23:39.627 --> 00:23:42.546 align:middle line:84%
She got out of that work
because when they did it.

00:23:42.546 --> 00:23:44.131 align:middle line:90%
When they announced it.

00:23:44.131 --> 00:23:45.215 align:middle line:90%
A guy named Taylor.

00:23:45.215 --> 00:23:46.842 align:middle line:84%
Who was a captain
at the time, who

00:23:46.842 --> 00:23:50.429 align:middle line:84%
was involved in these projects
for military intelligence,

00:23:50.429 --> 00:23:53.849 align:middle line:84%
basically said, you pursue
any of this, all your grants

00:23:53.849 --> 00:23:55.059 align:middle line:90%
and everything ends.

00:23:55.059 --> 00:23:56.435 align:middle line:90%
And they turned her grants off.

00:23:56.435 --> 00:23:57.603 align:middle line:90%
They turned everything off.

00:23:57.603 --> 00:23:57.978 align:middle line:90%
>> NOORY: Why?

00:23:57.978 --> 00:23:58.520 align:middle line:90%
>>BEGICH: Because--

00:23:58.520 --> 00:23:59.772 align:middle line:90%
>> NOORY: What was he afraid of?

00:23:59.772 --> 00:24:02.066 align:middle line:84%
>>BEGICH: This was the most
threateningly thing of all,

00:24:02.066 --> 00:24:04.735 align:middle line:84%
because think about
electronic telepathy.

00:24:04.735 --> 00:24:09.156 align:middle line:84%
If you could transfer
artificially and perhaps

00:24:09.156 --> 00:24:11.575 align:middle line:84%
even enhance a
person's ability do you

00:24:11.575 --> 00:24:15.037 align:middle line:84%
that, you want to talk about
a transparent government,

00:24:15.037 --> 00:24:16.705 align:middle line:90%
this is the solution.

00:24:16.705 --> 00:24:19.833 align:middle line:84%
The next evolution of humankind,
that level of transparency

00:24:19.833 --> 00:24:22.211 align:middle line:84%
is going to demand something
that our country needs right

00:24:22.211 --> 00:24:23.921 align:middle line:90%
now, and that's forgiveness.

00:24:23.921 --> 00:24:25.631 align:middle line:84%
We're going to have
to forgive ourselves,

00:24:25.631 --> 00:24:26.715 align:middle line:84%
we're going have to
forgive each other,

00:24:26.715 --> 00:24:28.342 align:middle line:84%
and we're going to
have to move forward

00:24:28.342 --> 00:24:30.427 align:middle line:90%
in a very different direction.

00:24:30.427 --> 00:24:32.262 align:middle line:84%
And the opportunity
we face in the country

00:24:32.262 --> 00:24:34.973 align:middle line:84%
now in an environment
of fear and anxiety

00:24:34.973 --> 00:24:37.976 align:middle line:84%
is to recognize that
is our adversary

00:24:37.976 --> 00:24:40.521 align:middle line:84%
and our only
adversary, to eliminate

00:24:40.521 --> 00:24:42.189 align:middle line:84%
the dialogue the
country needs to have

00:24:42.189 --> 00:24:43.273 align:middle line:90%
and we all need to have.

00:24:43.273 --> 00:24:45.192 align:middle line:84%
Mind control is not
about someone else

00:24:45.192 --> 00:24:46.527 align:middle line:90%
controlling our minds.

00:24:46.527 --> 00:24:48.487 align:middle line:84%
It's about us
controlling our minds,

00:24:48.487 --> 00:24:50.072 align:middle line:84%
us ushering in
the next evolution

00:24:50.072 --> 00:24:51.073 align:middle line:90%
and the next revolution.

00:24:51.073 --> 00:24:52.533 align:middle line:84%
>> NOORY: That's
what it should be.

00:24:52.533 --> 00:24:54.827 align:middle line:84%
>>BEGICH: That's what it
has to be if this is going

00:24:54.827 --> 00:24:56.370 align:middle line:90%
to really change the world.

00:24:56.370 --> 00:25:00.416 align:middle line:84%
Otherwise, we just repeat
the same cycle again

00:25:00.416 --> 00:25:03.293 align:middle line:84%
with a different set of actors,
a different set of players,

00:25:03.293 --> 00:25:07.256 align:middle line:84%
but the same net result. Freeing
the mind to our own potential

00:25:07.256 --> 00:25:08.632 align:middle line:90%
is where the answers lie.

00:25:08.632 --> 00:25:10.300 align:middle line:90%
Each of us has that potential.

00:25:10.300 --> 00:25:12.219 align:middle line:84%
Every major revolution,
every evolution

00:25:12.219 --> 00:25:13.971 align:middle line:84%
is started with one
or two people thinking

00:25:13.971 --> 00:25:16.640 align:middle line:84%
a little differently, whether
it's in art, science, business,

00:25:16.640 --> 00:25:17.474 align:middle line:90%
politics.

00:25:17.474 --> 00:25:18.851 align:middle line:90%
The same is true today.

00:25:18.851 --> 00:25:21.854 align:middle line:84%
We need a higher caliber of
leaders that engage the mind.

00:25:21.854 --> 00:25:24.940 align:middle line:84%
They use the mind in a way
that's not for manipulation,

00:25:24.940 --> 00:25:26.942 align:middle line:84%
but to enhance our
performance so we can make

00:25:26.942 --> 00:25:28.402 align:middle line:90%
better collective judgments.

00:25:28.402 --> 00:25:29.653 align:middle line:90%
That's what changes the world.

00:25:29.653 --> 00:25:32.948 align:middle line:84%
>> NOORY: In a perfect world,
Nick, that would be great.

00:25:32.948 --> 00:25:35.409 align:middle line:90%
But they're going to abuse this.

00:25:35.409 --> 00:25:36.201 align:middle line:90%
Aren't they?

00:25:36.201 --> 00:25:37.244 align:middle line:84%
>>BEGICH: There's
a lot of abuse.

00:25:37.244 --> 00:25:39.204 align:middle line:84%
And here's what's exciting
from my perspective.

00:25:39.204 --> 00:25:41.415 align:middle line:84%
A lot of the great research
that's coming out of this

00:25:41.415 --> 00:25:42.791 align:middle line:90%
isn't in governmental labs.

00:25:42.791 --> 00:25:45.169 align:middle line:84%
There's a lot of independent
people figuring this out.

00:25:45.169 --> 00:25:46.503 align:middle line:90%
And you see more and more of it.

00:25:46.503 --> 00:25:47.921 align:middle line:84%
And the other thing
I would say is

00:25:47.921 --> 00:25:49.214 align:middle line:90%
it's not about the technology.

00:25:49.214 --> 00:25:51.341 align:middle line:84%
These are natural
attributes that we all have

00:25:51.341 --> 00:25:52.551 align:middle line:90%
that we can enhance.

00:25:52.551 --> 00:25:54.261 align:middle line:84%
And there's lots of
disciplines out there

00:25:54.261 --> 00:25:56.513 align:middle line:90%
that lead us in that direction.

00:25:56.513 --> 00:25:59.099 align:middle line:84%
And I think we're going to see
more of that as time moves on.

00:25:59.099 --> 00:26:01.643 align:middle line:90%
And it doesn't take a mob.

00:26:01.643 --> 00:26:03.604 align:middle line:90%
It only takes a few.

00:26:03.604 --> 00:26:04.438 align:middle line:90%
And that's it.

00:26:04.438 --> 00:26:07.316 align:middle line:84%
And every major thing that's
ever happened on this planet

00:26:07.316 --> 00:26:10.444 align:middle line:84%
happened with a few seeing it
just a little bit differently.

00:26:10.444 --> 00:26:12.070 align:middle line:90%
And I think that's what we need.

00:26:12.070 --> 00:26:14.990 align:middle line:84%
We need leadership that can see
it a little bit differently.

00:26:14.990 --> 00:26:17.284 align:middle line:84%
But we also need to
recognize technologies

00:26:17.284 --> 00:26:19.286 align:middle line:90%
are sort of the backdrop.

00:26:19.286 --> 00:26:22.331 align:middle line:84%
We always try to duplicate
nature with our technology.

00:26:22.331 --> 00:26:25.083 align:middle line:84%
But some of these things that
we naturally have maybe are off

00:26:25.083 --> 00:26:26.376 align:middle line:90%
limits or should be off limits.

00:26:26.376 --> 00:26:29.129 align:middle line:84%
Controlling other people's
thought processes, in my view,

00:26:29.129 --> 00:26:30.339 align:middle line:90%
should be off limits.

00:26:30.339 --> 00:26:33.175 align:middle line:84%
Owning our digital data
in terms of the internet.

00:26:33.175 --> 00:26:34.635 align:middle line:84%
No longer is your
personal life--

00:26:34.635 --> 00:26:35.636 align:middle line:90%
>> NOORY: It's not ours.

00:26:35.636 --> 00:26:36.303 align:middle line:90%
>>BEGICH: No.

00:26:36.303 --> 00:26:36.762 align:middle line:90%
>> NOORY: It's not ours.

00:26:36.762 --> 00:26:38.514 align:middle line:84%
>>BEGICH: You go
into your house,

00:26:38.514 --> 00:26:40.933 align:middle line:84%
and your house is your
home of privacy, right?

00:26:40.933 --> 00:26:42.100 align:middle line:84%
Everything in it is
supposed to be private.

00:26:42.100 --> 00:26:42.768 align:middle line:90%
>> NOORY: Supposed to be.

00:26:42.768 --> 00:26:43.936 align:middle line:90%
>>BEGICH: Right.

00:26:43.936 --> 00:26:49.024 align:middle line:84%
Today, your digital doorway is
your house in the 21st century.

00:26:49.024 --> 00:26:51.693 align:middle line:84%
And this generation needs
to protect that house

00:26:51.693 --> 00:26:54.321 align:middle line:84%
as much as you protected the
threshold of your doorway.

00:26:54.321 --> 00:26:56.323 align:middle line:84%
>> NOORY: God knows
what they know about us.

00:26:56.323 --> 00:26:56.865 align:middle line:90%
>>BEGICH: Exactly.

00:26:56.865 --> 00:26:57.699 align:middle line:90%
And they shouldn't.

00:26:57.699 --> 00:26:59.910 align:middle line:84%
And commercial interests
shouldn't have it, either.

00:26:59.910 --> 00:27:01.745 align:middle line:84%
And once a transaction
is complete

00:27:01.745 --> 00:27:04.331 align:middle line:84%
and the ability to dispute
the transaction is complete,

00:27:04.331 --> 00:27:05.499 align:middle line:90%
the data ought to be wiped.

00:27:05.499 --> 00:27:07.668 align:middle line:84%
And they ought not to be
able to get our permission.

00:27:07.668 --> 00:27:08.377 align:middle line:90%
>> NOORY: But it's not.

00:27:08.377 --> 00:27:09.086 align:middle line:90%
>>BEGICH: No, it's not.

00:27:09.086 --> 00:27:09.545 align:middle line:90%
>> NOORY: But it's not.

00:27:09.545 --> 00:27:11.713 align:middle line:84%
>>BEGICH: And this
is, again, the change

00:27:11.713 --> 00:27:14.383 align:middle line:84%
in our technology, which
has been used to manipulate.

00:27:14.383 --> 00:27:16.969 align:middle line:84%
No one is standing up for the
little guy, which is again

00:27:16.969 --> 00:27:19.596 align:middle line:84%
where that anger comes from that
we see across the country in so

00:27:19.596 --> 00:27:20.514 align:middle line:90%
many different areas.

00:27:20.514 --> 00:27:22.558 align:middle line:84%
No one is standing
up for little guy.

00:27:22.558 --> 00:27:23.392 align:middle line:90%
They rationalize it.

00:27:23.392 --> 00:27:24.935 align:middle line:84%
Oh, we need it for
national security.

00:27:24.935 --> 00:27:26.562 align:middle line:84%
We need it for better
commercial sales.

00:27:26.562 --> 00:27:28.272 align:middle line:84%
We need it for this,
we need it for that.

00:27:28.272 --> 00:27:31.108 align:middle line:84%
What we need is the maintenance
of our personal liberty

00:27:31.108 --> 00:27:32.526 align:middle line:84%
and freedom so that
we can continue

00:27:32.526 --> 00:27:35.737 align:middle line:84%
to have a productive
dialogue and maybe get back

00:27:35.737 --> 00:27:38.657 align:middle line:84%
to a more productive dialogue,
not just in this country,

00:27:38.657 --> 00:27:39.533 align:middle line:90%
but around the world.

00:27:39.533 --> 00:27:41.869 align:middle line:84%
What we saw in the United
States is not unique.

00:27:41.869 --> 00:27:44.538 align:middle line:84%
This is happening
in every place I go.

00:27:44.538 --> 00:27:46.248 align:middle line:84%
On one level or
another, people are

00:27:46.248 --> 00:27:48.584 align:middle line:84%
angry because we've
been forgotten.

00:27:48.584 --> 00:27:51.587 align:middle line:84%
And it's time to wake
up in a different way

00:27:51.587 --> 00:27:53.046 align:middle line:84%
with a different
consciousness, not

00:27:53.046 --> 00:27:55.424 align:middle line:84%
one based on anger
and fear, but based

00:27:55.424 --> 00:27:58.927 align:middle line:84%
on thinking, based on progress,
and recognizing that today we

00:27:58.927 --> 00:28:00.888 align:middle line:84%
can even group fund
individual work.

00:28:00.888 --> 00:28:03.390 align:middle line:84%
There's people getting funding
for projects that would never

00:28:03.390 --> 00:28:04.892 align:middle line:90%
have gotten funding before.

00:28:04.892 --> 00:28:06.852 align:middle line:84%
There's lots of
opportunity for change

00:28:06.852 --> 00:28:08.896 align:middle line:84%
as much as there
is for disaster.

00:28:08.896 --> 00:28:11.023 align:middle line:84%
And whenever you see
the pendulum swinging

00:28:11.023 --> 00:28:13.358 align:middle line:84%
this far in one direction,
it's the opportunity

00:28:13.358 --> 00:28:14.943 align:middle line:90%
to swing it back the other way.

00:28:14.943 --> 00:28:17.738 align:middle line:84%
>> NOORY: Nick, let's look
at how this can be applied

00:28:17.738 --> 00:28:22.242 align:middle line:90%
to medical applications.

00:28:22.242 --> 00:28:24.077 align:middle line:90%
>> Capsule has magnets inside.

00:28:24.077 --> 00:28:28.165 align:middle line:84%
